These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-7-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, cain, siglo, oliveros, aristoff, alhambra, dannemann
The people use 7 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, subway, motorbike, skateboard, van, bike
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, board-games, filmmaking, baking, singing, drawing, collecting
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: drawingpy, balloon-flower, amaryllis, daffodil, dahlia, lily, begonia
 1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 5. the person who growslily is in an even position##4
 6. the cain-smoker is the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person who growsdahlia and the person driving the airplane##7
 8. the person who growsdahlia is the cain-smoker##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsdahlia##7
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
12. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
13. the person driving the bike is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the scooter##7
14. the person who growsdrawingpy is in the middle##1
15. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
16. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
17. the person who growsdrawingpy is the person driving the motorbike##1
18. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
19. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
20. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
21. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who's hobby is singing##1
22. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
23. the siglo-smoker is not the person who growsbegonia##6
24. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the alhambra-smoker##1
25. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3       |     4      |    5     |    6     |       7       |
| Cigar      | aristoff  | alhambra   | dannemann        | oliveros      | montecristo      | siglo | cain |
